The paper discusses the security and privacy concerns of Business Intelligence (BI) as a service on Cloud computing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also talks about the multilayered model of BI and Cloud computing, which involves networking (cs.NI), distributed computing (cs.DC), and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper proposes an algorithm for ensuring multi-level session inspections, which involves software engineering (cs.SE).
